atex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>τ</mi><mi>θ</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\tau_{\\theta}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5806em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.1132em;\">τ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.1132em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 可以将多样的条件模态转化为潜在表示：</p><ul>\n<li>文本描述：\"一只猫坐在沙发上 (a cat sitting on a sofa)\" (文本模态)</li>\n<li>语义分割图：用颜色标记图像中不同区域的类别 (图像模态)</li>\n<li>边界框：物体在图像中的位置和类别信息 (结构化数据)</li>\n<li>类别标签 : \"猫 (cat)\", \"狗 (dog)\" (离散类别)</li>\n</ul></div></details></p>\n<p>具体来说</p>\n<div class=\"math math-display\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">Q</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">W</mi><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">Q</mi><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo fence=\"true\">)</mo></mrow></msubsup><mo>⋅</mo><msub><mi>φ</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">(</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">z</mi><mi>t</mi></msub><mo fence=\"true\">)</mo></mrow><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mspace width=\"1em\"></mspace><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">K</mi><mo>=</mo><m